Package: GeneExpressionAnalysis
Title: Gene Expression Analysis and Clustering
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Andrine", "Risøy", , "andrinerisoy@icloud.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Andrine Risøy [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Andrine Risøy <andrinerisoy@icloud.com>
Description: Analyzes and clusters gene expression data from common 
    formats using Bioconductor data structures. The package provides normalization,
    clustering, visualization and gene set enrichment analysis.
